# .npmrc - Homey App publish config
# CRITICAL: omit=optional prevents heavy CI-only deps (puppeteer, sharp, canvas)
# from being installed by the Athom Docker publish container (npm ci --ignore-scripts).
# Without this, the archive was inflated to 48.72MB causing Athom processing_failed.
# These deps are only needed for local development scripts, not for the app runtime.
omit=optional
